'''''The Best is Yet to Come''''' was a film distributed by [[exploitation film]] presenter [[Kroger Babb]] in 1951. Babb promoted the film as "all there is to know about cancer".
==References== {{Reflist}}
* ''New York Times'': Specialist. 18 March 1951. * [[John Waters (filmmaker)|John Waters]], "[http://www.landmarktheatres.com/mn/dirtyshame.html My Kind of Guy]" (URL accessed 16 October 2006). * Mike Quarles: ''Down and Dirty: Hollywood's Exploitation Filmmakers and Their Movies''. McFarland & Company, 2001.
